Standards-Version: 3.9.1

Package: indi-aagcloudwatcher-ng
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libindi1
Description: INDI driver for the AAG Cloud Watcher (new api version and anemometer support)
 INDI driver for the AAG Cloud Watcher using the new INDI Weather API and with anemometer support
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.

Package: indi-aagcloudwatcher-ng-dbg
Priority: extra
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Depends: indi-aagcloudwatcher-ng (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: INDI driver for the AAG Cloud Watcher
 INDI driver for the AAG Cloud Watcher
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.
 This package contains the debug symbols for the this driver, useful to investigate problems in INDI.
